{"id":1734,"date":"2019-09-25T04:48:43","date_gmt":"2019-09-25T04:48:43","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/99rockingtees.teesbank.website\/?page_id=1734"},"modified":"2022-06-20T03:37:48","modified_gmt":"2022-06-20T03:37:48","slug":"fly-removal","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/fly-removal\/","title":{"rendered":"Fly removal"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1734\" class=\"elementor elementor-1734\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2b2d9ce elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"2b2d9ce\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-df33e5b\" data-id=\"df33e5b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f7393b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2f7393b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">FLY REMOVAL PEST CONTROL<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-05f9a76 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"05f9a76\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p>Flies can be immensely annoying and keep ruining your relaxation time during day and night. These pests will keep landing on food, annoy your visitors and generally cause a discomfort. No matter how many flies you kill with a flyswatter, you will still have new flies to deal with! In order to stop flies from disturbing you, you need a professional fly removal service by ACME.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d7d1537 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"d7d1537\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1020\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/flies-cropped-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3847\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/flies-cropped-1.jpg 1020w, https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/flies-cropped-1-300x118.jpg 300w, https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/flies-cropped-1-768x301.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a865701 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a865701\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Flies are not only annoying they can be extremely harmful for your health as well. House flies can spread over 65 serious diseases, as stated by the world health organization. Some of the diseases flies can carry are:<\/p><ul><li class=\"aio-icon-title ult-responsive\" data-ultimate-target=\"#Info-box-wrap-9494 .aio-icon-title\" data-responsive-json-new=\"{\">Cholera<\/li><li class=\"aio-icon-title ult-responsive\" data-ultimate-target=\"#Info-box-wrap-6843 .aio-icon-title\" data-responsive-json-new=\"{\">Salmonellosis (also known as Salmonella)<\/li><li>Tuberculosis<\/li><li class=\"aio-icon-title ult-responsive\" data-ultimate-target=\"#Info-box-wrap-9772 .aio-icon-title\" data-responsive-json-new=\"{\">Conjunctivitis<\/li><li>Gastroenteritis<\/li><li>Dysentery<\/li><li class=\"aio-icon-title ult-responsive\" data-ultimate-target=\"#Info-box-wrap-6658 .aio-icon-title\" data-responsive-json-new=\"{\">Typhoid fever<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-665bfa5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"665bfa5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">In addition, you can easily get skin and eye infections without a timely fly removal from your property.<\/h5>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a2e39eb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a2e39eb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p>Flies commonly feed on decaying and rotting matter, in addition to animal and human feces. Therefore, once a fly feast on infected food, it can transmit the same bacteria to your food. For that reason, if you notice a fly landing on your food, you shouldn\u2019t keep eating it. Instead, we recommend you to throw that food away as it can be infected with bacteria. The same way if a fly lands on your cooking cutlery and\/or utensils, make sure to wash those items carefully before using them again.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"vc_separator wpb_content_element vc_separator_align_center vc_sep_width_100 vc_sep_border_width_2 vc_sep_pos_align_center vc_sep_color_juicy_pink vc_separator-has-text\">\u00a0<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-478c0c7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"478c0c7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">CONTACT OUR PEST CONTROL TEAM<\/h5>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dbacc7f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dbacc7f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p>At ACME, we provide the most innovative fly removal solutions in (AREA). We will not only remove the flies from your house but we will ensure they stay away after we leave. Our team of knowledgeable technicians uses the most efficient methodologies for a fly removal. As a team we will not leave behind any substances that could harm you or your pets. Thus, you can safely continue your day-to-day activities without any flies interrupting you.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-67290d8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"67290d8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22780162_198012460742502_174594672038647781_n-1-768x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-3389\" alt=\"Pest Control Truck Milton\" srcset=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22780162_198012460742502_174594672038647781_n-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22780162_19